ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.team11

Class HistoricalFitnessData

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.team11.HistoricalFitnessData

  • public class HistoricalFitnessData
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains this user's fitness data from all past days and from today, accolades earned, it also store the users lifetime totals and best days for particular fitness data items. Note: some getter/setter methods are never called and only were created in the early stages of the project to allow serialization of this Object. This idea was later scrapped but the methods are still here in case we change our mind
    Author:
    Team 11
